title: Ep. 616 - Selfish Babies
description:
Today on the Matt Walsh Show, a restaurant owner in L.A. has her business shut down even as a Hollywood studio is setting up catering tents right next door. Meanwhile, actors on SNL and talking heads on CNN lecture lockdown protesters for being selfish “babies.” We’ll talk about who the real selfish babies are. And Five Headlines, including the Chicago Teachers Union claiming that it’s racist and sexist to reopen schools, and a doctor in Oregon has his license revoked for criticizing masks.
